===Benefactor, I'd like to...===
{{Messages
|start_condition = 
|text =
:'''Tingyun:''' Benefactor, I'd like to ask you something
:{Choice} What is it?
:'''(Trailblazer):''' What is it?
:'''Tingyun:''' This may be disrespectful, but I'm very curious...
:'''Tingyun:''' Is the Express really here just to help the Xianzhou Luofu solve the Stellaron problem?
:{Choice} Yes. Why?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Is it really that hard to understand why the Express is here? Can't someone act simply out of the kindness of their heart?
:{Choice} What are you trying to say?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Is it really that hard to understand why the Express is here? Can't someone act simply out of the kindness of their heart?
:'''Tingyun:''' After all, people who help others without thinking of compensation or risks during the dangerous trips across the cosmos is rarer than air in vacuum
:'''Tingyun:''' When the higher-ups of Xianzhou first heard of your reasons for coming, they thought you were here either to seek immortality or the Stellaron...
:{Choice} Seek immortality?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Seeking immortality is absolutely forbidden on the Xianzhou, no?
::'''Tingyun:''' Yes. As the home of long-life species, countless Elixir Seekers from all corners of the universe come to the Xianzhou to re-enact bygone histories and discover the secret of the Xianzhou residents' immortality
:{Choice} Seek the Stellaron?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Stellarons are the seeds of ruin. Why would the Express want the Stellaron?
::'''Tingyun:''' But not everyone in the cosmos thinks this way. As a seed dispersed by an Aeon, some desire to obtain its power regardless of the cost
:'''Tingyun:''' Apologies, I may have crossed the line. I don't know why I said all this
:'''Tingyun:''' I have absolute trust in your sincerity, benefactor, but the powerful masters are bound to think more than a pawn like me
:'''Tingyun:''' So, please be careful...
}}
