===Say, did you see that, benefactor?===
{{Messages
|start_condition = 
|text =
:'''Tingyun:''' Say, did you see that, benefactor?
:'''Tingyun:''' When the Ebon Deer's stomped the ground, branches sprouted out of nowhere
:{Choice} I saw
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Those must be... the Ambrosial Arbor's roots?
:{Choice} Branches?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Those must be... the Ambrosial Arbor's roots?
:'''Tingyun:''' The celestial traces of Abundance are indeed marvelous to behold
:'''Tingyun:''' This is the first time I've seen something so miraculous among all my travels
:'''Tingyun:''' The fruits on those boughs are sparkling gold, just like what the Xianzhou legends say
:'''Tingyun:''' It is said that in ancient times, the forebears of the Xianzhou received immortal fruits like this of the Ambrosial Arbor and turned into long-life species
:'''Tingyun:''' If I were to eat this fruit, would I obtain endless life just like the Xianzhou natives...?
:'''Tingyun:''' Are you not tempted by such a chance, benefactor?
:{Choice} A dangerous thought...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Miss Tingyun, wouldn't you be breaching the Xianzhou ban?
::'''Tingyun:''' Ahh
::'''Tingyun:''' Please pardon me for my rudeness and my little test
::'''Tingyun:''' As I thought, you are an honest and righteous person, benefactor
:{Choice} Can't leave if you eat it...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' If you eat this fruit, I'm afraid you won't get to live for a thousand years... but executed by the Cloud Knights moments after.
::'''Tingyun:''' You're right, benefactor
::'''Tingyun:''' But if you manage to get past the Cloud Knights' searches
::'''Tingyun:''' This opportunity seems too good to pass up, right?
:{Choice} Oh, I was tempted...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Then... Miss Tingyun... did you save a fruit?
::'''Tingyun:''' If I say yes, would you want to share it with me, benefactor?
:'''Tingyun:''' But I thank you for the thought, benefactor
:'''Tingyun:''' Unfortunately, the Ebon Deer is now dust, and no fruit of the Ambrosial Arbor is left behind
:'''Tingyun:''' Such opportunities are extremely rare, but they slip away in the blink of an eye.
:'''Tingyun:''' Just like life itself...
}}
